title: 239. Andy & DJ CTI: Dave Chappelle Not Canceled, Australia Fully Reopened? & Iran Slams Suppressing Peaceful Protest
itunes:title: 239. Andy & DJ CTI: Dave Chappelle Not Canceled, Australia Fully Reopened? & Iran Slams Suppressing Peaceful Protest
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ discuss Dave Chappelle's new Netflix deal allowing him to produce four comedy specials after controversy following his last special, Australia welcoming international tourists for the first time in two years, and Iran slamming Canada for not allowing peaceful protests.
